content:
When you set up the CRM Analytics for Communication Business app, you have access to various datasets for gaining valuable insights into your business.

Available in: Developer edition and for an extra cost in Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.

CRM Analytics for Communications-Business app includes the following datasets:

Account
Opportunity
Oppty Products
Orchestration Item
Order
OrderItem
plain_quota
Quota
Quote
QuoteMember
User

The plain_quota dataset is optional and must be imported from a CSV source. Upload this dataset to view relevant metrics in the Home dashboard.
title: Understanding CRM Analytics for Communications-Business App Datasets
